{"tid":200524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華文傳媒柒到喊！聯合航空被虐越裔乘客代表律師：事件與種族無關","createTime":"2017-04-14T04:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T06:25:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4dce253c2016daa3059fe86d085920c01c68d7bb","tid":200524,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T04:51:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1325140-20170414.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1325140-20170414.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=41dc1fc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1325140-20170414.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=43cd036c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1325140-20170414.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國聯合航空強行把乘客拖落機事件，事主透過律師表示，遭遇比在越戰的經歷更可怕。<br />\n<br />\n69歲的事主來自越南，在美國任職醫生，其家人和代表律師召開記者會。<br />\n<br />\n律師說，當事人兩隻門牙脫落，鼻樑骨折，並有明顯腦震盪，已於當地周三晚出院，打算接受重建手術。<br />\n<br />\n律師表明將提出訴訟，已經向伊利諾伊州法院緊急申請，在下星期一舉行聽證之前，要求航空公司和管理芝加哥機場的市政府保存證據，包括閉路電視片段、駕駛艙通話紀錄和乘客及機組人員名單。<br />\n<br />\n雖然事主是亞裔人，律師認為<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">事件與種族無關</span></strong>，又指航空公司，尤其聯合航空長時間欺凌乘客。<br />\n<br />\n事主的女兒稱，對父親的遭遇感到恐懼、震驚和厭惡。她說，無論在任何情況下，在父親身上發生的事，都不應該發生在任何人身上。<br />\n<br />\n聯合航空行政總裁穆尼奧斯早前就事件致歉，承諾不會再發生把乘客強行拖落機事件。<br />\n<br />\n聯合航空又說，將為事發航機上所有乘客安排退票。"},{"pid":"4186599cb244559834debd5c84b3a89f7dd3fb0f","tid":200524,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T04:55:37.000Z","msg":"港台新聞都改稱返個醫生係越南裔<br />\n<br />\n毒果日報到今日都仍然要屈人「華裔」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170414/19990087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170414%2F19990087&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=307c83e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170414%2F19990087&h=53724149\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170414/19990087</a>"},{"pid":"4a9bb639a88dd33cbfefee40d052c25295afdcf3","tid":200524,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T04:57:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港台新聞都改稱返個醫生係越南裔<br />\n<br />\n毒果日報到今日都仍然要屈人「華裔」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170414/19990087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170414%2F19990087&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=307c83e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170414%2F19990087&h=53724149\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170414/19990087</a></blockquote><br />\nCCTVB尋晚都講緊華裔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c9ca2937340a00a7bf4943ec7ce72c7c1a52ef","tid":200524,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T04:58:12.000Z","msg":"咪信啦<br />\n試下黑人夠唔夠薑拉人落機"},{"pid":"22ce7ba74d27ae14c09c706f31900a450824238f","tid":200524,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T05:00:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪信啦<br />\n試下黑人夠唔夠薑拉人落機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n白人坐頭等FULL PAID:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/198342/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flihkg.na.cx%2Fthread%2F198342%2Fpage%2F1&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=ff8ddbb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/198342/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c1ea23116b41a9b6c7283ab4d6aaddd82c4e8675","tid":200524,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T05:02:06.000Z","msg":"黑眼睛 黑頭髮 黃皮膚就係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"