70497630ad95b5a","tid":200524,"uid":29938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T05:32:23.000Z","msg":"仲喺度老屈人係華裔嗰啲先係真正嘅種族歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820b67067ae2c6952459f036a4d6b798e6c84468","tid":200524,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T05:43:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>港台新聞D用字已經變返中肯<br />\n呢D咪專業囉</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1325109\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1325109&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=9f092a3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1325109&h=31bfc8ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1325109</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>被強行拖下飛機事主據報擬向聯合航空提出訴訟</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2017-04-13 HKT 21:51<br />\n<br />\n美國聯合航空有乘客被強行拖下機的事件。69歲來自越南，在美國任職醫生的事主，向傳媒首度開腔，指身心受創仍留醫。他已聘請律師向聯合航空提出索償，要求航空公司及芝加哥政府，保留出事當日的閉路電視片段、機艙錄音等資料。<br />\n<br />\n聯合航空行政總裁穆尼奧斯再次就事件致歉，稱對事件感到「羞愧」，但表明不會辭職。航空公司又宣布，向肇事航班所有乘客提供全額退款。<br />\n<br />\n有網民在白宮網站請願，要求聯邦政府調查事件，短時間內已累積超過20萬人聯署。"},{"pid":"edbc870137955411a70e4c564bcf36a73b38fedf","tid":200524,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T05:45:03.000Z","msg":"全球華亞裔都是中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f4b6cbec95d569595504d05e953ee853acd5d0","tid":200524,"uid":26942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T05:51:20.000Z","msg":"証明媒體洗腦幾有用 好似唱首龍的傳人咁 黃皮膚就係中國撚"},{"pid":"03971b3edf1030b56d6e7096fc3631233a2d78f1","tid":200524,"uid":93839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,